                <strong>Matrix Multiplication:</strong> Row √ó Column (dot product)<br>
                <strong>Matrix Transpose:</strong> Swap rows and columns
            </div>

            <div class="key-points">
                <h3>üéØ Key Points to Remember:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Matrix = Table/grid of numbers in rows and columns</li>
                    <li>Addition = Add numbers in same position</li>
                    <li>Multiplication = Multiply rows by columns</li>
